# Sinnet.top — SEO & GEO Optimization Guide

This repository provides a comprehensive optimization roadmap for [sinnet.top](https://sinnet.top), a tennis-tech brand combining an AI coach app with factory-direct gear. The guide focuses on both **traditional SEO** (Google, Bing, Baidu) and **GEO** (Generative Engine Optimization for LLMs like ChatGPT, DeepSeek, Gemini).

